<br>
   One thing to remember is that US copyright law is not as hard and fast as criminal law.  I can not tell you for certain whether a given work is actually in violation or not; this matter is decided in court.  Consequently, if you keep the matter out of the courts, you can not be found to be in violation of the law.<br>
